caption.text:
This new browser can take actions for you, and it‚Äôs a glimpse into the future of how we use the internet.

It‚Äôs called Comet, by Perplexity.

Comet is an agentic browser that integrates AI natively.

So for example, you could:

- Ask it to open new tabs for credible web pages about upcoming movies
- While watching a YouTube video ask it to summarize it and include all the links it references
- Ask it to draft a professional email declining the latest job offer in your gmail
- Look at stock charts and ask it to identify support and resistance
- Unsubscribe from all marketing emails
- Ask it to find the last hat you bought on Amazon and order another one

You get the point.

The browser wars are getting started.

Who do you think comes out on top?

Also, shout out to @garyvee and the crew at @veefriends for the hat. It‚Äôs dope!

If you like this video, follow¬†@rpn to stay two steps ahead on the incredibly disruption happening in tech and how to leverage it in content and business.
